overview:
Online technology has now advanced to the point where the Internet no longer represents a restriction on the interaction and encounter between two parties. On the contrary, we expect 24-Rapid Response, with all its benefits and opportunities, to be a major venue for future coaching, training and therapy says Steinar Brevik Knudsen, founder of this innovative service.

24-Rapid Response exists to connect those who want help with those who help.

In so doing, we hope to be an excellent information resource for consumers, and to connect prospective counseling clients to counseling professionals 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year.

We are committed to setting standards for electronic counseling and care, as well as providing a quality resource for persons to find excellent mental health professionals in their local areas.
